<<timed 5s t8n>>
<p>Sunset will be at 3:50 p.m. today and, as per Civil Defence regulations, everyone must comply with the regulations to mask their windows, skylights, and entrances to comply with blackout regulations 30 minutes before sunset: 3:20 p.m.</p>

<p>To make sure that they have enough basic supplies (such as milk and tobacco), after lunch some members of the household go to Greenep’s Tobacco and Sweet Shop to confirm the information that they have, gather any final information from their neighbours and maybe even air raid wardens or first aid workers who might also stop by.</p>

<<next 3s>>
<p>They return with whatever additional facts, anecdotes, and even rumours they have heard at the shop.</p>

<p>More tea is brewing, and [[someone has made some scones.|SelectHousehold3]]</p>

